<abstract><t>This draft describes the solution of inter-as option-B connection between NVO3 network and MPLS/IP VPN network. The ASBR located in NVO3 network is called ASBR-d, the control plane and data plane procedures at ASBR-d are specified in this document, there are some differences from traditional option-B ASBR defined in [RFC 4364].</t></abstract>

